&lt;li&gt;Independently investigate, design, and execute solutions across distributed systems with a high degree of ambiguity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect, build, and maintain highly available, scalable REST APIs and backend services for internal and external use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive system decoupling, modularization, and technical debt reduction — improving long-term maintainability without blocking near-term delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build agentically as your default: leveraging concurrent autonomous agent workflows, owning the output, and keeping a steady queue of aligned work moving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay at the forefront of emerging AI tooling and practices, bringing new techniques back to the team and helping raise the floor for how Postscript engineers work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to how we think about integrating AI into our systems and workflows — not just using AI tools, but helping shape where and how AI creates leverage across the engineering org&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with product, data, and go-to-market teams — communicating clearly and proactively in an async-first environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and eliminate single points of failure, improving system resilience and knowledge redundancy across your team&lt;/li&gt;
